Title: 37. Seeking the seekers
Text:
I need to find messengers who traveled towards Darkwell Empire border.
Instructions:
1. Sail east towards opposite shore.
2. Sail south towards entrance to the Great marsh.
3. Sail east through Great marsh, until there is bigger island to my right.
4. From the isle, I should continue on foot south untill I get nearby big forest.
5. Turn back and return to Aramoor.
CompleteText:
The camp is empty, but there are traces of blood around!
I need to investigate.
